sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant S as Session Server
  participant O as Generation Orchestrator
  participant H as LLMHub
  participant W as Worker
  participant A as Asset Store (S3/CDN)

  C->>S: spawn prompt
  S->>O: createJob(prompt, context)
  S-->>C: spawn placeholder (proxy asset)
  O->>H: generate structured recipe
  H-->>O: recipe + model trace
  O->>W: run generation plan
  W->>H: image/3D calls
  H-->>W: outputs
  W->>W: postprocess + validate
  W->>A: upload GLB + textures
  O-->>S: job ready + assetId
  S-->>C: asset_ready(assetId)
  C->>A: fetch asset
